            <fr:title text="Forester 4.1">Forester 4.1</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Release</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>Special thanks to <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/kentookura.xml" title="Kento Okura" addr="forest://forester/kentookura" type="local">Kento Okura</fr:link>, <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/nickhu.xml" title="Nick Hu" addr="forest://forester/nickhu" type="local">Nick Hu</fr:link>, and <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/treborhuang.xml" title="Trebor Huang" addr="forest://forester/treborhuang" type="local">Trebor Huang</fr:link> for their contributions to this release.</html:p>
